be. It is essential to partner with a company for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/mobile-app-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mobile app development services<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Here_are_some_interesting_statistics\"><\/span>Here are some interesting statistics<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Mobile apps are expected to generate a whopping <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/topics\/1002\/mobile-app-usage\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">$189 billion<\/a> in revenue by 2020.<\/li>\n<li>The Apple App Store has 2.2 million apps available for download.<\/li>\n<li>There are around 2.8 million apps available for download on the Google Play Store.<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/themanifest.com\/app-development\/mobile-app-usage-statistics-2018\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">21% of Millennials<\/a> open an app 50+ times per day.<\/li>\n<li>49% of people open an app 11+ times each day.<\/li>\n<li>57% of all digital media use occurs from mobile apps.<\/li>\n<li>The average smartphone owner uses 30 apps each month.<\/li>\n<li>Apple app store dominate the market in terms of consumer spending, taking <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/259510\/revenue-distribution-between-the-apple-app-store-and-google-play\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">a 64 percent share of worldwide consumer spending on app stores<\/a>.<\/li>\n<li>By 2023, mobile apps are expected to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/269025\/worldwide-mobile-app-revenue-forecast\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">generate over 9935 billion U.S. dollars through paid downloads and in-app advertising<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Is it possible to outshine competitors with the mobile app? With millions of apps across the Google PlayStore or the iOS app store, the key to success in the app world is an innovative idea. Will your mobile app solve the problems of users?<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/latest-software-testing-trends-the-rise-of-managed-qa-services-in-2020.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mobile app developers<\/a> can infuse life into business ideas, bringing it to life. Hence, several organizations are looking to hire app developers who can build a mobile app that can increase customer engagement levels.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Most_popular_iOS_App_Store_categories\"><\/span>Most popular iOS App Store categories<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Launched in 2008, the number of apps available in the App store has continually increased since its inception. Gaming apps are the most popular apps based on availability, as about 25 percent of all apps available fit in this category.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter pdimgauto wp-image-7300\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/popular-iOS-App-Store-categories.png\" alt=\"popular iOS App Store categories\" width=\"680\" height=\"515\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/popular-iOS-App-Store-categories.png 680w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/popular-iOS-App-Store-categories-300x227.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Top_Android_App_categories\"><\/span>Top Android App categories<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This statistics gives information on the market reach of the most popular Android app categories worldwide as of September 2019. During the period, it was discovered that travel and local content apps had a 95.73 percent reach among global Android mobile users.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter pdimgauto wp-image-7299\"